# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Submission-prep & stale docs — kept LOCAL only, never on the public repo.
# These present as a ready-to-submit package (cover letter, submission guide,
# manuscript.pdf) although no submission exists yet, and would mislead visitors.
# Maintain them on your machine; add to the repo only once a real preprint/paper
# ID exists. See also RELEASE_NOTES.md "Paper & preprint" (honest, no-ID policy).
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
